ntent": "[quote][pid=864095477,45974302,3632]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60098113]水墨有痕[/uid] (2026-04-10 12:37):[/b]<br/><br/>靠的就是小丑人设吃流量，据说他的会员群，一个月能收入上百万，不知真假[/quote]<br/>我靠  全市场只有我是被白嫖的？还一直被白嫖好几年？", "lou": 1961, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 864095477, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775795919}, {"pid": 864103477, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 45, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 13:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "这里为什么要清仓啊。。。。如果周末继续TACO或者继续搁置延期 <br/>你们不是炸了？完全不理解这里为什么要清仓。", "lou": 1962, "content_length": 100, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775800415}, {"pid": 864103757, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 18, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 13:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864103598,45974302,3641]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67118720]真的被恶心到了[/uid] (2026-04-10 13:54):[/b]<br/><br/>能问下狼大这里留多少仓位么[/quote]<br/>55%-60%啊  收盘的时候<br/>盘中看情况加减  但是最后是这个仓位", "lou": 1963, "content_length": 56, "reply_to": 864103598, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775800560}, {"pid": 864104732, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 38, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 14:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "市场在给你们买点了[s:ac:哭笑] 笑死了 怕大家不敢买", "lou": 1964, "content_length": 34, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775801082}, {"pid": 864105858, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 14:14", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864104990,45974302,3643]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66955584]11145800666a[/uid] (2026-04-10 14:06):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:喷]狼大太神了。[/quote]<br/>你们真是小看我了 这点程度不值得吹嘘<br/>之前我甚至可以虚空画第二天的线。", "lou": 1965, "content_length": 71, "reply_to": 864104990, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775801673}, {"pid": 864108902, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 21, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 14:39", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864108560,45974302,3646]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=43274930]zhaoxzksima[/uid] (2026-04-10 14:36):[/b]<br/><br/>以后再也不会进商业航天股票了，三进三出全部被俘虏，命里不和[s:ac:哭1][/quote]<br/><br/>[img]./mon_202604/10/jmQ2x-adv1K7ToS5g-3x.jpg[/img]<br/>我觉得商航非常好[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 1966, "content_length": 55, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202604/10/jmQ2x-adv1K7ToS5g-3x.jpg", "size": 8, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202604/10", "name": "jmQ2x-adv1K7ToS5g-3x.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "24"}], "reply_to": 864108560, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775803187}, {"pid": 864109594, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 23, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 14:45", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "刚才下午4000点附近应该大概是300来E增量   一半应该是散户[s:ac:哭笑]", "lou": 1967, "content_length": 50, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775803530}, {"pid": 864110317, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 14:50", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864110178,45974302,3648]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67143809]Rzzz二号机[/uid] (2026-04-10 14:49):[/b]<br/><br/>[s:ac:哭笑]dsjm里面到底有什么脏东西，我真服了，除了章还有其他的吗[/quote]<br/>他们老板就是最大的脏东西", "lou": 1968, "content_length": 29, "reply_to": 864110178, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775803858}, {"pid": 864110614, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 50, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 14:53", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864110366,45974302,3649]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65607716]8muses[/uid] (2026-04-10 14:51):[/b]<br/><br/>我和你们观点相反，我觉得市场已经交易谈判成功了，就算真谈成了，大概率给冲个4020也要回落，所以今天进去没啥性价比，最多留着底仓就可以了。[/quote]<br/>要是交易谈判成功现在大盘是4200  你信不信<br/>老美能接受那10条随便一条  万斯就是李鸿章第二", "lou": 1969, "content_length": 85, "reply_to": 864110366, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775804004}, {"pid": 864111724, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 8192, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 15:01", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[img]./mon_202604/10/jmQ2x-joigK4T8S2i-42.jpg[/img]<br/>反正我不知道你们 我是这样的仓位收盘", "lou": 1970, "content_length": 70, "attachs": [{"attachurl": "mon_202604/10/jmQ2x-joigK4T8S2i-42.jpg", "size": 4, "type": "img", "subid": 0, "url_utf8_org_name": "image%2epng", "dscp": "", "path": "mon_202604/10", "name": "jmQ2x-joigK4T8S2i-42.jpg", "ext": "jpg", "thumb": "8"}], "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775804511}, {"pid": 864111891, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 17, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-10 15:03", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864111382,45974302,3650]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=65607716]8muses[/uid] (2026-04-10 14:59):[/b]<br/><br/>那要看咋定义谈判成功，我觉得市场交易的谈判后继续停火就算成功。[/quote]<br/>谈判 搁置 打  谈判  搁置 不打<br/>不打的时候市场马上可以交易TACO 哪怕后面再打也无所谓了", "lou": 1971, "content_length": 79, "reply_to": 864111382, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775804580}, {"pid": 864320769, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 87, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-12 16:40", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "减完仓是不是周末能睡着了[s:ac:哭笑]<br/>甚至磨拳擦掌周一要大干进去？<br/>目前星期一低开概率已经达到91.23%", "lou": 1972, "content_length": 82, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775983258}, {"pid": 864322336, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 36, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-12 17:00", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864321453,45974302,3666]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=60916468]灰兔尾[/uid] (2026-04-12 16:49):[/b]<br/><br/>没谈成是预料之中的中性事件，只要交战范围还控制在黎巴嫩区域就还符合停火预期，周一如果低开，高走的概率不小，但是充其量也就继续震荡而已；最近做了不少调研，我发现美国很可能在藏兵，目前地面部队的集结数量可能超出了原本估计的数量，后面看二次交火之后的战果来判断走向吧[/quote]<br/>算是小利空吧  因为第一次谈判没有对二次谈判有任何预期和希望 正常来说会第一次谈判后会出现双方的核心诉求。目前没看见任何消息<br/>反正肯定是个低开，至于能不能高走还要看别的市场，我们目前是机构自救，而且已经过了4000没什么太大的主观向上动能<br/>做好预期后先观察至少半天再说。", "lou": 1973, "content_length": 261, "reply_to": 864321453, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775984414}, {"pid": 864324497, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 44, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-12 17:25", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864324281,45974302,3666]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=64289495]生鱼片是死鱼片wk[/uid] (2026-04-12 17:23):[/b]<br/><br/>干进去是不是会死了狼大[s:ac:晕][/quote]<br/>意思就是不要急 先观察 <br/>有先手的优势就是涨了能追 跌了能补  如果你开盘就干进去 那你和上周打满的有什么区别 白白把先手优势丢掉", "lou": 1974, "content_length": 119, "reply_to": 864324281, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1775985932}, {"pid": 864383808, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 57, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-13 09:54", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "借低开加了点  暂时目标看到4030-4035", "lou": 1975, "content_length": 33, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776045244}, {"pid": 864384174, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 12, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-13 09:56", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864383887,45974302,3677]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=67138594]旋律27720[/uid] (2026-04-13 09:54):[/b]<br/><br/>终于轮到我flh扬眉吐气了[/quote]<br/>但是我宏和已经板了啊  复材也超过10%了。。。3代目前还没体现  确实暂时不如二代", "lou": 1976, "content_length": 77, "reply_to": 864383887, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776045399}, {"pid": 864394106, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 22, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-13 11:04", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864393882,45974302,3685]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=40319180]SaikaDeath[/uid] (2026-04-13 11:03):[/b]<br/><br/>看游戏砸了这么多在研究有没有能建仓的然后看了一眼巨人网络，一个股票走势能垃圾成这样也是没谁了[/quote]<br/>巨人的营收有一半是 中东那边的DB游戏<br/>现在那边在打仗啊 。。。。", "lou": 1977, "content_length": 63, "reply_to": 864393882, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776049479}, {"pid": 864395442, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 19, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-13 11:13", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864394624,45974302,3685]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=66983776]大时代冲冲冲[/uid] (2026-04-13 11:07):[/b]<br/><br/>这么说来，游戏也是战争受损板块了，和民航一样可以博弈停战反弹了[/quote]<br/>只有巨人是这样而已 其他大部分还是跟AI软 属于跌得比AI软少一点  涨也少一点", "lou": 1978, "content_length": 73, "reply_to": 864394624, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776049982}, {"pid": 864414969, "fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "authorid": 150058, "type": 0, "score": 25, "score_2": 0, "recommend": 0, "postdate": "2026-04-13 13:48", "subject": "", "alterinfo": "", "content": "[quote][pid=864414594,45974302,3695]Reply[/pid] [b]Post by [uid=36912645]Binah[/uid] (2026-04-13 13:45):[/b]<br/><br/>不进锂的一大原因就是缺德时代这个锂版特锂普，各个方面都真恶心啊[s:ac:哭笑][/quote]<br/>可以不做锂 做电池一样的 今年下半年首批固态电池量产", "lou": 1979, "content_length": 53, "reply_to": 864414594, "from_client": "0 /", "postdatetimestamp": 1776059330}], "__T": {"fid": 706, "tid": 45974302, "topic_misc": null, "subject": "自立自强，科学技术打头阵", "locked": 0, "recommend": 0, "quote_to": null, "quote_from": 0, "type": 36, "replies": 155489, "authorid": 150058, "postdate": 1768179906, "lastpost": 1782109303, "jdata": null, "author": "-阿狼-", "lastposter": "异乡猫", "digest": 0, "lastmodify": 1782109315, "tpid": 0, "post_misc_var": {"content_length": 412, "fid": 706, "comment_id": ",854270755,860174433", "14": {"17": 1, "14": 4, "13": 4, "12": 1}, "16": "63335896,19412700,26652007,67067074,20672033,66881586,67068843,66199622,60819388,60409766,67057614,60264977,61082281,42701832,66998841,61574956,61272875,6708